# Specs Directory

This directory contains project specifications created by Spec Kit.

## Usage

When using Spec Kit for complex development tasks, specifications will be automatically generated and stored here.

## Example Structure

```
specs/
├── feature-user-auth.md          # User authentication feature spec
├── api-payment-integration.md    # Payment API integration spec
├── database-schema-v2.md         # Database schema update spec
└── performance-optimization.md   # Performance improvement spec
```

## Template

Use the `templates/spec-template.md` as a starting point for new specifications.